            "text": " into how Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis oversaw a billion-dollar transfer of state employees‚Äô retirement dollars into high-fee, high-risk private equity firms, as the companies‚Äô executives donated to groups supporting his campaigns. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
