          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " a bill to DeSantis‚Äô desk that would allow a 50 percent increase in the amount of state pension money that could be allocated to private equity, hedge funds and private real estate. The California Public Employees Retirement System, the country‚Äôs largest pension fund, has an ‚Äú",
            "type": "text",
