          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Actual change ultimately depends on the level of public outrage over private equity‚Äôs massive level of influence in America today. While a few members of Congress have been vocal on the issue, it is difficult for these concerns to break through to the wider public, especially given the corporate media‚Äôs reticence to cover this issue in depth. That‚Äôs why it‚Äôs all the more important that we have outlets like ",
